.

1. *Hrabrosti* nije vezana samo za ratne podvige, već se može pokazati i u svakodnevnom životu. (Bravery is not only related to war exploits, it can be also shown in everyday life.) 
2. On nije izgubio *hrabrost*, već je samo smatrao da nije promenio svoju situaciju. (He didn't lose his courage, he just thought he hadn't changed his situation.)
3. Ona je pokazala *hrabrost* u trenutku kada je drugi oklijevali. (She showed courage at the moment when others hesitated.)
4. Njegova *hrabrost* se pokazala u činjenici da je i dalje nastavio da boravi u tom gradu, iako je bilo očigledno da je opasno. (His bravery was shown by the fact that he kept staying in that city, even though it was obvious it was dangerous.)
5. Oni su zahvaljujući svojoj *hrabrosti* uspeli da izađu na kraj sa svim problemima. (Thanks to their courage, they managed to cope with all the problems.)